header(class="sticky top-0 z-20 border-b border-zinc-200 bg-white/95 backdrop-blur dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-950/95")
    div(class="flex flex-col gap-3 px-5 py-4 md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between")
        div
            div(class="flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-medium text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400")
                i(class="fa-solid fa-gear")
                span System
            h1(class="mt-1 text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") 시스템 설정
        button(type="button", (click)="load()", class="inline-flex h-9 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-zinc-300 bg-white px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
            i(class="fa-solid fa-rotate-right")
            span 새로고침

main(class="space-y-5 px-5 py-5")
    div(*ngIf="loading()", class="h-32 rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white p-5 text-sm text-zinc-500 dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-400") 정보를 불러오는 중입니다.
    div(*ngIf="error()", class="rounded-md border border-rose-200 bg-rose-50 px-4 py-3 text-sm text-rose-700 dark:border-rose-900/70 dark:bg-rose-950/40 dark:text-rose-300") {{error()}}

    div(*ngIf="!loading() && !error()", class="space-y-5")
        div(class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2 border-b border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-800")
            button(*ngFor="let item of tabItems()", type="button", (click)="setActiveTab(item.key)", class="inline-flex h-10 items-center gap-2 border-b-2 px-3 text-sm font-semibold transition-colors", [ngClass]="activeTab() === item.key ? 'border-zinc-950 text-zinc-950 dark:border-zinc-100 dark:text-zinc-50' : 'border-transparent text-zinc-500 hover:text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-400 dark:hover:text-zinc-100'")
                i(class="fa-solid", [ngClass]="item.icon")
                span {{item.label}}

        section(class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-5")
            div(*ngIf="activeTab() === 'general'", class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900")
                div(class="border-b border-zinc-200 px-4 py-3 dark:border-zinc-800")
                    h2(class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") General
                    p(class="mt-1 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 브라우저 제목, favicon, 사이드바 로고를 저장 시 한 번에 적용합니다.
                div(class="space-y-4 p-4")
                    label(class="block")
                        span(class="mb-1 block text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 브라우저 제목
                        input(type="text", data-testid="system-browser-title", [(ngModel)]="general.browser_title", class="h-10 w-full rounded-md border border-zinc-300 bg-white px-3 text-sm text-zinc-900 focus:border-zinc-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-1 focus:ring-zinc-500 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-100")

                    div(class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 p-4 dark:border-zinc-800")
                        div(class="flex items-start justify-between gap-3")
                            div
                                p(class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") 관리자 비밀번호
                                p(class="mt-1 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") Docker Infra 로그인 비밀번호
                            i(class="fa-solid fa-lock text-zinc-400")
                        div(class="mt-4 grid grid-cols-1 gap-3 md:grid-cols-3")
                            label(class="block")
                                span(class="mb-1 block text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 현재 비밀번호
                                input(type="password", data-testid="system-admin-current-password", autocomplete="current-password", [(ngModel)]="adminPassword.current_password", class="h-10 w-full rounded-md border border-zinc-300 bg-white px-3 text-sm text-zinc-900 focus:border-zinc-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-1 focus:ring-zinc-500 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-100")
                            label(class="block")
                                span(class="mb-1 block text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 새 비밀번호
                                input(type="password", data-testid="system-admin-new-password", autocomplete="new-password", [(ngModel)]="adminPassword.new_password", class="h-10 w-full rounded-md border border-zinc-300 bg-white px-3 text-sm text-zinc-900 focus:border-zinc-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-1 focus:ring-zinc-500 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-100")
                            label(class="block")
                                span(class="mb-1 block text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 새 비밀번호 확인
                                input(type="password", data-testid="system-admin-confirm-password", autocomplete="new-password", [(ngModel)]="adminPassword.confirm_password", (keyup.enter)="changeAdminPassword()", class="h-10 w-full rounded-md border border-zinc-300 bg-white px-3 text-sm text-zinc-900 focus:border-zinc-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-1 focus:ring-zinc-500 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-100")
                        button(type="button", data-testid="system-admin-password-save", (click)="changeAdminPassword()", [disabled]="savingPassword()", class="mt-3 inline-flex h-10 w-full items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-zinc-300 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 disabled:opacity-60 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
                            i(class="fa-solid", [ngClass]="savingPassword() ? 'fa-spinner fa-spin' : 'fa-key'")
                            span {{savingPassword() ? '변경 중...' : '관리자 비밀번호 변경'}}

                    div(class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-4 md:grid-cols-2")
                        div(class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 p-4 dark:border-zinc-800")
                            div(class="flex items-start justify-between gap-3")
                                div
                                    p(class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") Favicon
                                    p(class="mt-1 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") SVG, PNG, ICO를 지원합니다.
                                div(class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-zinc-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-950")
                                    img([src]="previewUrl('favicon')", alt="favicon", class="h-8 w-8 rounded object-contain")
                            input(id="system-favicon-upload", type="file", accept=".ico,.png,.svg,.gif,.jpg,.jpeg,.webp", class="hidden", (change)="selectAsset('favicon', $event)")
                            div(class="mt-3 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2")
                                button(type="button", (click)="openAssetPicker('system-favicon-upload')", class="inline-flex h-9 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-zinc-300 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
                                    i(class="fa-solid fa-image")
                                    span 이미지 선택
                                button(*ngIf="hasPendingAsset('favicon')", type="button", (click)="clearSelectedAsset('favicon')", class="inline-flex h-9 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-rose-300 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-rose-700 hover:bg-rose-50 dark:border-rose-900/70 dark:text-rose-300 dark:hover:bg-rose-950/30")
                                    i(class="fa-solid fa-xmark")
                                    span 선택 취소
                            p(class="mt-2 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400")
                                span(*ngIf="hasPendingAsset('favicon')") {{pendingAssetName('favicon')}} 파일을 선택했습니다. 저장 시 업로드됩니다.
                                span(*ngIf="!hasPendingAsset('favicon')") Favicon 경로는 고정되어 있으며 새 이미지를 저장하면 기존 파일을 대체합니다.
                        div(class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 p-4 dark:border-zinc-800")
                            div(class="flex items-start justify-between gap-3")
                                div
                                    p(class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") Sidebar Logo
                                    p(class="mt-1 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 좌측 메뉴 상단에 표시되는 브랜드 이미지
                                div(class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center overflow-hidden rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-zinc-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-950")
                                    img(*ngIf="previewUrl('logo')", [src]="previewUrl('logo')", alt="logo", class="h-full w-full object-contain")
                                    span(*ngIf="!previewUrl('logo')", class="text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-400") 없음
                            input(id="system-logo-upload", type="file", accept=".png,.svg,.gif,.jpg,.jpeg,.webp", class="hidden", (change)="selectAsset('logo', $event)")
                            div(class="mt-3 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2")
                                button(type="button", (click)="openAssetPicker('system-logo-upload')", class="inline-flex h-9 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-zinc-300 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
                                    i(class="fa-solid fa-image")
                                    span 이미지 선택
                                button(*ngIf="hasPendingAsset('logo')", type="button", (click)="clearSelectedAsset('logo')", class="inline-flex h-9 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-rose-300 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-rose-700 hover:bg-rose-50 dark:border-rose-900/70 dark:text-rose-300 dark:hover:bg-rose-950/30")
                                    i(class="fa-solid fa-xmark")
                                    span 선택 취소
                            p(class="mt-2 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400")
                                span(*ngIf="hasPendingAsset('logo')") {{pendingAssetName('logo')}} 파일을 선택했습니다. 저장 시 업로드됩니다.
                                span(*ngIf="!hasPendingAsset('logo')") Logo 경로는 고정되어 있으며 새 이미지를 저장하면 기존 파일을 대체합니다.

                    button(type="button", data-testid="system-general-save", (click)="saveGeneral()", [disabled]="savingGeneral()", class="inline-flex h-10 w-full items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-md bg-zinc-950 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white hover:bg-zinc-800 disabled:opacity-60 dark:bg-zinc-100 dark:text-zinc-950 dark:hover:bg-zinc-200")
                        i(class="fa-solid fa-floppy-disk")
                        span {{savingGeneral() ? '저장 중...' : '일반 설정 저장'}}

            div(*ngIf="activeTab() === 'backup'", class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900")
                div(class="flex items-start justify-between gap-3 border-b border-zinc-200 px-4 py-3 dark:border-zinc-800")
                    div
                        h2(class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") 서비스 백업 시스템
                        p(class="mt-1 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 이 장비의 내부 백업 저장소로 서비스 이미지 이력을 보관합니다.
                    span(class="inline-flex rounded-md border px-2 py-1 text-xs font-semibold", [ngClass]="backupSystem.status === 'running' ? 'border-emerald-200 bg-emerald-50 text-emerald-700 dark:border-emerald-900/70 dark:bg-emerald-950/40 dark:text-emerald-300' : backupSystem.status === 'failed' ? 'border-rose-200 bg-rose-50 text-rose-700 dark:border-rose-900/70 dark:bg-rose-950/40 dark:text-rose-300' : 'border-zinc-200 bg-zinc-50 text-zinc-600 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-300'") {{backupStatusLabel()}}
                div(class="space-y-4 p-4")
                    div(*ngIf="!backupSystem.installed", class="space-y-4")
                        div(class="flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between")
                            div
                                p(class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") 백업 시스템이 아직 설치되지 않았습니다.
                                p(class="mt-1 text-xs leading-5 text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 설치를 시작하면 진행 로그가 아래에 표시됩니다.
                            button(type="button", (click)="installBackupSystem()", [disabled]="backupInstalling()", class="inline-flex h-10 items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-md bg-zinc-950 px-4 text-sm font-semibold text-white hover:bg-zinc-800 disabled:opacity-60 dark:bg-zinc-100 dark:text-zinc-950 dark:hover:bg-zinc-200")
                                i(class="fa-solid", [ngClass]="backupInstalling() ? 'fa-spinner fa-spin' : 'fa-download'")
                                span {{backupInstalling() ? '설치 중' : '백업 시스템 설치'}}
                        div(*ngIf="backupSystem.last_error", class="rounded-md border border-rose-200 bg-rose-50 px-3 py-2 text-sm text-rose-700 dark:border-rose-900/70 dark:bg-rose-950/40 dark:text-rose-300") {{backupSystem.last_error}}
                        div(*ngIf="backupInstallVisible()", class="overflow-hidden rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-zinc-950 dark:border-zinc-800")
                            div(class="flex items-center justify-between border-b border-zinc-800 px-3 py-2")
                                p(class="text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-100") 설치 진행
                                span(class="text-xs font-semibold", [ngClass]="backupInstallDone() ? (backupInstallOperation?.status === 'succeeded' ? 'text-emerald-300' : 'text-rose-300') : 'text-zinc-400'") {{backupInstallStatusLabel()}}
                            pre(class="max-h-80 min-h-40 overflow-auto whitespace-pre-wrap px-3 py-3 font-mono text-xs leading-5 text-zinc-100") {{backupInstallOutput()}}
                    div(*ngIf="backupSystem.installed", class="space-y-4")
                        div(class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-3 md:grid-cols-2")
                            div(class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 px-3 py-3 dark:border-zinc-800")
                                p(class="text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 백업 시스템 상태
                                p(class="mt-2 text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") {{backupStatusLabel()}}
                            div(class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 px-3 py-3 dark:border-zinc-800")
                                p(class="text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 상태 확인 결과
                                p(class="mt-2 text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") {{backupHealthLabel()}}
                        div(*ngIf="backupSystem.last_error", class="rounded-md border border-rose-200 bg-rose-50 px-3 py-2 text-sm text-rose-700 dark:border-rose-900/70 dark:bg-rose-950/40 dark:text-rose-300") {{backupSystem.last_error}}
                        div(class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2")
                            button(type="button", (click)="refreshBackupSystem()", [disabled]="backupBusy()", class="inline-flex h-10 items-center gap-2 rounded-md bg-zinc-950 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white hover:bg-zinc-800 disabled:opacity-60 dark:bg-zinc-100 dark:text-zinc-950 dark:hover:bg-zinc-200")
                                i(class="fa-solid", [ngClass]="backupBusy() ? 'fa-spinner fa-spin' : 'fa-heart-pulse'")
                                span 상태 확인
                            button(type="button", (click)="applyBackupRegistryNodes()", [disabled]="backupNodeRegistryBusy()", class="inline-flex h-10 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-zinc-300 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 disabled:opacity-60 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
                                i(class="fa-solid", [ngClass]="backupNodeRegistryBusy() ? 'fa-spinner fa-spin' : 'fa-network-wired'")
                                span 노드 설정 적용
                            button(type="button", (click)="runBackupAction('start')", [disabled]="backupBusy() || backupSystem.status === 'running'", class="inline-flex h-10 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-zinc-300 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 disabled:opacity-60 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
                                i(class="fa-solid fa-play")
                                span 시작
                            button(type="button", (click)="runBackupAction('restart')", [disabled]="backupBusy()", class="inline-flex h-10 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-zinc-300 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 disabled:opacity-60 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
                                i(class="fa-solid fa-rotate")
                                span 재시작
                            button(type="button", (click)="runBackupAction('stop')", [disabled]="backupBusy() || backupSystem.status !== 'running'", class="inline-flex h-10 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-rose-300 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-rose-700 hover:bg-rose-50 disabled:opacity-60 dark:border-rose-900/70 dark:text-rose-300 dark:hover:bg-rose-950/30")
                                i(class="fa-solid fa-stop")
                                span 정지
                            button(type="button", (click)="runBackupAction('disable')", [disabled]="backupBusy() || backupSystem.status === 'disabled'", class="inline-flex h-10 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-amber-300 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-amber-700 hover:bg-amber-50 disabled:opacity-60 dark:border-amber-900/70 dark:text-amber-300 dark:hover:bg-amber-950/30")
                                i(class="fa-solid fa-power-off")
                                span 비활성화
                        div(class="overflow-hidden rounded-md border border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-800")
                            div(class="grid gap-3 border-b border-zinc-200 bg-zinc-50 px-4 py-4 dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-950/60 lg:grid-cols-[1fr_auto]")
                                div(class="flex items-start gap-3")
                                    div(class="flex h-10 w-10 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-md bg-white text-zinc-700 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-zinc-200 dark:bg-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:ring-zinc-800")
                                        i(class="fa-solid fa-calendar-check")
                                    div
                                        h3(class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") 서비스 이미지 자동 백업
                                        p(class="mt-1 text-xs leading-5 text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") {{backupScheduleSummary()}}
                                div(class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2 lg:justify-end")
                                    span(class="inline-flex rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white px-2 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-600 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-300") 마지막 실행 {{backupPolicyLastRunLabel()}}
                                    span(*ngIf="backupPolicy.enabled", class="inline-flex rounded-md border border-emerald-200 bg-emerald-50 px-2 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-emerald-700 dark:border-emerald-900/70 dark:bg-emerald-950/40 dark:text-emerald-300") 사용 중
                                    span(*ngIf="!backupPolicy.enabled", class="inline-flex rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white px-2 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-400") 꺼짐
                            div(class="p-4")
                                label(class="flex min-h-12 items-center justify-between gap-4 rounded-md border px-3 py-2 transition-colors", [ngClass]="backupPolicy.enabled ? 'border-emerald-200 bg-emerald-50/70 dark:border-emerald-900/70 dark:bg-emerald-950/30' : 'border-zinc-200 bg-white dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900'")
                                    span(class="flex items-center gap-3")
                                        span(class="flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-md bg-white text-zinc-700 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-zinc-200 dark:bg-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:ring-zinc-800")
                                            i(class="fa-solid", [ngClass]="backupPolicy.enabled ? 'fa-toggle-on text-emerald-600 dark:text-emerald-300' : 'fa-toggle-off text-zinc-400'")
                                        span
                                            span(class="block text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100") 자동 백업 사용
                                            span(class="mt-0.5 block text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") {{backupRetentionSummary()}}
                                    input(type="checkbox", [(ngModel)]="backupPolicy.enabled", class="h-4 w-4 shrink-0 rounded border-zinc-300 text-zinc-950 focus:ring-zinc-500 dark:border-zinc-700")
                                div(*ngIf="backupPolicy.enabled", class="mt-4 space-y-4")
                                    div(class="grid gap-4 lg:grid-cols-[1.3fr_0.7fr]")
                                        div(class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white p-3 dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900")
                                            div(class="mb-3 flex items-center justify-between gap-3")
                                                p(class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") 실행 일정
                                                span(class="text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") {{backupScheduleSummary()}}
                                            div(class="inline-flex rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-zinc-50 p-1 dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-950")
                                                button(*ngFor="let item of backupScheduleTypes()", type="button", (click)="setBackupScheduleType(item.key)", class="inline-flex h-8 items-center gap-2 rounded px-3 text-xs font-semibold transition-colors", [ngClass]="backupPolicy.schedule_type === item.key ? 'bg-white text-zinc-950 shadow-sm dark:bg-zinc-800 dark:text-zinc-50' : 'text-zinc-500 hover:text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-400 dark:hover:text-zinc-100'")
                                                    i(class="fa-solid", [ngClass]="item.icon")
                                                    span {{item.label}}
                                            div(*ngIf="backupPolicy.schedule_type === 'weekly'", class="mt-3")
                                                span(class="mb-2 block text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 실행 요일
                                                div(class="grid grid-cols-7 gap-1.5")
                                                    button(*ngFor="let day of weekdayOptions()", type="button", (click)="setBackupWeekday(day.value)", class="h-9 rounded-md border text-xs font-semibold transition-colors", [ngClass]="backupPolicy.schedule_weekday == day.value ? 'border-zinc-950 bg-zinc-950 text-white dark:border-zinc-100 dark:bg-zinc-100 dark:text-zinc-950' : 'border-zinc-200 bg-white text-zinc-600 hover:bg-zinc-50 dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-300 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800'") {{day.label}}
                                            div(class="mt-3 grid grid-cols-1 gap-3 sm:grid-cols-2")
                                                label(*ngIf="backupPolicy.schedule_type === 'monthly'", class="block")
                                                    span(class="mb-1 block text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 실행 날짜
